 |publisher    = SLAC
 |accessdate   = 2009-10-06
 |archive-date = 2020-01-29
 |archive-url  = https://web.archive.org/web/20200129040920/http://www-library.desy.de/cgi-bin/spiface/find/blu/hep/wwwcite?rawcmd=FIND+COLLABORATION+SNO+and+topcite+500%2B
 |dead-url     = yes
}}</ref>2007年，{{le|富蘭克林學院|Franklin Institute}}頒授物理學的[[富蘭克林獎章|富蘭克林獎章]]給SNO主任[[阿瑟·麥克唐納|阿瑟·麥克唐納]]<ref>
{{cite web
 |title       = Arthur B. McDonald, Ph.D.
